prompt.title: Embedding for AI-Friendly Markup: Book Language
prompt.content: The Book language is a human-understandable markup language for writing AI applications such as chatbots, knowledge bases, agents, avatars, translators, and automations. It is based on markdown and designed to be easily readable and writable without requiring specific technical knowledge.
